item.title: Aspose.PUB for .NET 23.12 Release Notes
item.description: This page contains release notes for Aspose.PUB for .NET 23.12. Aspose.PUB for .NET is a сonvenient library that provides the feature to convert Microsoft Publisher documents. The library is in compliance with the .NET 5.0 and also supports .NET Standard 2.0, .NET Standard 2.1 and .NET Framework 4.0. .NET 6.0 target framework support has been added. You can use it for application development in any IDE that targets the .
